<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150892>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Bulbophyllum fenestratum. A. Flowering plant. B. Inflorescence. C. Flower bracts. D. Flower, viewa from different sides. E. Flower, with median sepal removed, side view. F. Dorsal sepal, abaxial and adaxial side. G. Lateral sepal, abaxial and adaxial side. H. Magnified margin of lateral sepal. I. Petal, adaxial and abaxial side. J. Lip, views from different sides. K. Pedicel, ovary column, and lip, side view. L & M. Column apex, half-side view. N. Column, side view. O. Anther cap, view from above and from below. P. Pollinaria.All photo by Truong Ba Vuong from specimen BV 1737, photo correction and design by L. Averyanov and T. Maisak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150892/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

